        Our intelligence engine calculates real-time AI displacement risks using global market data and predictive neural modeling.
      </p>

      <!-- Calculator Terminal -->
      <div class="bg-[#0d1120] border border-[#1e2340] rounded-2xl p-2 max-w-xl mx-auto neon-glow">
